# NAME: SierraChart
# AUTHOR: Kevin (kevshen13)
# REPO: https://github.com/kevshen13/surge-rules
# DESCRIPTION: Sierra Chart rule list for Surge
# UPDATED: 2026-04-22
# MAINTENANCE: Maintain this list by traffic purpose and route behavior.
# RULE: Include Sierra Chart platform processes, official domains, and related simulation or download endpoints.
# RULE: Keep broad keyword rules conservative and only where Sierra Chart consistently relies on them.
# SOURCE: Sierra Chart docs list official data-service ports, server hostnames, IPs, and Denali regional overrides.

PROCESS-NAME,SierraChart
PROCESS-NAME,Sierra Chart
DOMAIN,www.sierrachart.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,sierrachart.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,sierracharts.com
DOMAIN,denali.sierrachart.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,dtcprotocol.org
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,futurestrading
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,tradesimulation
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ddfplus.com

# ==================== Denali CME Regional Overrides ====================
# Tokyo for East Asia, Germany for Europe, New Zealand for Asia-Pacific/Oceania.
DOMAIN,ds45.sierracharts.com
DOMAIN,ds14-2.sierracharts.com
DOMAIN,ds40.sierracharts.com

